@startuml
' @id(CMP-VIEWER-RENDER-PIPELINE)
' @ref(USE-VIEW-DIAGRAMS)
' Current-side component view after the font fix: the font database is a
' populated dependency owned at the usvg boundary, fed by shared_fontdb().
title mdd-viewer render pipeline — ownership (current)

actor "Developer" as Dev

component "mdd-cli\nCommands::View" as Cli
component "mdd-viewer\nMddViewer (eframe::App)\nDiagramPage, shared_fontdb()" as Viewer
component "mdd-core\nProject, ModelRegistry, Trace" as Core
folder ".mdd/rendered/\n(pre-rendered SVG)" as Rendered
folder ".mdd/models/, .mdd/trace.yml" as Models

package "SVG rasterization (external crates)" {
  component "usvg 0.44\nOptions { fontdb, font_family }" as Usvg
  component "fontdb 0.22\n(system fonts loaded once)" as FontDb
  component "resvg 0.44 +\ntiny-skia 0.11" as Resvg
}
component "eframe / egui 0.30\n(window, painter, textures)" as Egui

Dev --> Cli : mdd view
Cli --> Viewer : run(project)
Cli --> Core : Project::discover
Viewer --> Core : model_registry(), read_trace()
Core --> Models : scan
Viewer --> Rendered : read SVG bytes
Viewer --> FontDb : shared_fontdb() (OnceLock, once)
Usvg --> FontDb : resolves <text> font families
Viewer --> Usvg : Tree::from_data(Options { fontdb, ..default() })
Usvg --> Resvg : tree
Resvg --> Viewer : RGBA pixmap (glyphs rasterized)
Viewer --> Egui : texture + painter.image()
Egui --> Dev : on-screen diagram with legible text

note bottom of FontDb
  The font database lives HERE, not in egui.
  Loaded once via shared_fontdb()'s static
  OnceLock and Arc-cloned per parse. egui's
  `default_fonts` is a separate stack.
end note
@enduml
